&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for a Medical Secretary/Administrator within our Administration Team based at&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kingskerswell &amp; Ipplepen Health Centre &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; We invite enthusiastic, flexible and reliable candidates to apply to join our friendly, hardworking and high achieving Team to cover maternity leave on a fixed term contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role would ideally suit someone with experience in General Practice and especially those with a working knowledge of Systmone and Audio Typing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate should have proven secretarial experience including audio typing, minute taking, and experience using Microsoft applications. We are looking for candidates who have proven experience of working in a similar role and of working under pressure.  Applicants must have excellent customer service and administration skills.  A methodical and accurate approach to administrative work is essential for this role.&lt;/p&gt;
